{"tid":2098241,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣說服媽媽去睇心理/精神科醫生？:-(:-(","createTime":"2020-07-07T10:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T12:09:33.000Z","uid":162198,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8465049ecced922737c1f1ffe6b99611f53e56b9","tid":2098241,"uid":162198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"我呀媽五十頭，唔知係咪更年期定點，小小嘢就發哂爛咋，小則黑面，大則瘋狂bang門同無啦啦自己走咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有煲韓劇煲到我覺得係成癮，有時癲到全家一齊食佢自己一條友開個pad係度睇 試過向佢攤牌但最後佢又發脾氣咁收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位可以幫幫小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40599cb65c416e3c02b86107663ec9f72608099e","tid":2098241,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"建議最好先陪下佢做鍾意嘅嘢 同佢拉近左關係先再叫佢睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7351173a6ec0262588ffa3081f086dac8a02f0","tid":2098241,"uid":118354,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"盡量都唔好激嬲佢先就下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c9e80753d4f6eae8ddff2234c434ff1cd7d072","tid":2098241,"uid":162198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40599cb65c416e3c02b86107663ec9f72608099e","tid":2098241,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"建議最好先陪下佢做鍾意嘅嘢 同佢拉近左關係先再叫佢睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"喊出黎 仲記得幾年前發燒發到40度問佢點算好 佢淨係坐係度睇韓劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能因為咁而對佢呢個喜好反感"},{"pid":"2fbc109133f590